--- !u!114 &1615955909
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1615955907}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f4688fdb7df04437aeb418b961361dc5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_Material: {fileID: 0}
  m_Color: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
  m_RaycastTarget: 1
  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'They say everything you do comes back to you,

    In solemn echoes, where
    shadows construe.

    You, a traveler, in the cosmic expanse,

    Navigating
    realms of chance and circumstance.




    In the dance of shadows, where echoes
    persist,

    Seek the solace, let grace coexist.

    Empires rise, a testament
    to might,

    Yet, in their fall, a somber light.




    Greed''s allure, a
    transient song,

    In the cosmic symphony, where you belong.

    Guilt, a
    mirror reflecting deeds untold,

    In your journey, let the narrative unfold.




    Break
    the cycle, forge a path anew,

    In the abstract realms, where destinies accrue.

    Rise
    from shadows to the sublime,

    For you, Zagreus, will rewrite our time.













    VOICE
    ACTORS



    CHARLIE

    STEPHEN MULDERRY



    MYRA

    DANA BALIN



    MR.
    CLARKE

    DAVIS CLARKE



    THE ENGINEER

    JAMES SONG



    SYSTEM

    FRANK
    HU



    TECHNICIANS

    ALEX RIVAS

    RHYS DE HAAN

    JORDAN ZHAO

    SAM
    SAH-NIXON



    MISC.

    RAIHAN BHUIYA

    (MAYBE ONE/TWO MORE?)






    ARTWORK



    2D

    ZACH
    D''AMICO

    STEPHEN MULDERRY



    3D

    JAMES SONG

    DAVIS CLARKE



    CREATIVE
    COMMONS MODELS ON SKETCHFAB

    CURLYFRYWHY

    GUNNAR CORREA

    SAEED KHALILI

    OLLI_ONE

    SHEPDES

    ANKUSH
    GUPTA

    TRAIANDUMBRAVA

    LASSI KAUKONEN

    IROVETSKIY

    PERSIANTIGER

    THUNDER

    WILLIE
    EVENSSON



    CREATIVE COMMONS TEXTURES

    ISTOCKPHOTO

    FREEPIK

    PIXABAY

    PIXILART






    FONTS

    https://www.dafont.com/electronic-highway-sign.font

    https://www.dafont.com/a-dripping-marker.font

    LITTLEBOY






    MUSIC

    JAMES
    SONG



    "WINTER" BY ANTONIO VIVALDI






    AUDIO

    CREATIVE COMMONS
    AUDIO FROM PIXABAY

    APPLE SOUND EFFECTS






    CODING

    SAM SAH-NIXON

    RHYS
    DE HAAN

    JAMES SONG



    EXTERNAL SCRIPTS

    https://github.com/staffantan/unity-vhsglitch

    https://gist.github.com/ftvs/5822103






    ALPHA
    TESTING TEAM

    ARAV RAMASWAMY

    COLETTE SAWYER

    IRIS GU

    JAY DING






    SPECIAL
    THANKS

    HELIOS LUNG

    SEBASTIAN NOGUEIRA






    STORY AND GAME BY

    JAMES
    SONG






    MADE WITH UNITY AND BLENDER'
